sequenceDiagram
  participant B as Browser
  participant E as Express
  participant T as tRPC procedure
  participant D as DB
  B->>E: HTTP /api/trpc request
  E->>T: createContext authenticates session
  T->>T: protected/admin/editor/permission middleware
  T->>D: Drizzle/data-layer call
  D-->>T: rows/domain data
  T-->>B: SuperJSON response
